  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Oh, you have a Jewish problem?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What kind of Jewish problem do you have?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They make all the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They are controllers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said-- I never let him know I was Jewish-- tell me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Where does the Jew make the money-- how do you say?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Where does the non-Jew have the money that the Jew makes from?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because he has to make it from the non-Jew as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So where does the non-Jew have the money to make, where the Jew makes from the non-Jew?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, why do you feel that the Jewish people are a problem?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because they use their brains for survival?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I says, if you want to be rich, you can be rich.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Nobody stops you, nothing to do with religions, only what you think you want to decide what you want to do with your, your life.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I started to philosophize on Hitler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's when I gave that ceremony about the legacy that Hitler left behind is bottom line a constant reminder by the world that Germany has created and has finished off a genocide of a group of people, as well as gypsies, and all kinds of other people, that they felt didn't belong in their society.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, your children, and your children, and your children, everybody is going to suffer the implication of that genocide because that man kept you weak by implicating the Jew as the wrong person.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I says, when you take one side to use as a weapon and keep you down in a weak spot so that he can fulfill his dreams, he victimized both sides.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One, he exterminated.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
